data.description: Come see this beautiful house with creek front property!! Best of both worlds with 1.64 acres of country living & a neighborhood vibe. Such a great location in Quitman close to shopping & schools. Fall mornings on the front porch or late evenings on the deck watching the deer come up make this home the perfect place to create memories. Step inside this beautiful 3bed/2bath home & take in the family friendly layout. Just imagine being able to hangout around the kitchen island & chat with your friends & family while the game is on in the Great Room. Tons of natural light, plenty big enough for your sectional couch and room for the kids to play makes this such a functional space. Let's talk about how big the Master Suite is...big enough for a king & a walk in closet fit for a queen! Private bath w/double sink vanity is a must have. Stroll down the hall to the 2 kids bedrooms. Both are very spacious, lovely flooring and share a hall bath. Let's chat laundry, after all we spend plenty of time in there and this space checks all the boxes with cabinets, storage space & a folding table. It's Picture Perfect! Fenced yard, livestock welcome, chicken coop/mini shed and gorgeous woods!
